ygData.subject: RE: [eqbards] soloing strategies
ygData.msgSnippet: The skeleton tower in Lake of Ill Omen is the best place for mid-twenties soloing I ever saw.  I made 31 from 26 there fairly quickly with only grouping
ygData.messageBody:
The skeleton tower in Lake of Ill Omen is the best place for mid-twenties
soloing I ever saw. I made 31 from 26 there fairly quickly with only
grouping side-trips to Dalnir's and Frontier Mts.

Kitasi

-----Original Message-----
From: onur.yildirim@... [mailto:onur.yildirim@...]
Sent: Wednesday, April 18, 2001 2:26 PM

Subject: [eqbards] soloing strategies
